2003-05-24  James Youngman <jay@gnu.org>

	* po/da.po, de.po, es.po, et.po, findutils.pot, fr.po, gl.po,
	id.po, it.po, ko.po, nl.po, pl.po, pt_BR.po, ru.po, sv.po, tr.po:
	also need stpcpy (e.g. for Solaris)

